Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.09,0:00:04.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Never forgive...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.98,0:00:08.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Never forgive...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.41,0:00:16.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the leader of the 7 Kin of Purgatory, Ultear!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.77,0:00:18.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on, rotten daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.02,0:00:23.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna teach you a lesson in your mother's place!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.85,0:01:57.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultear!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.87,0:02:00.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.64,0:02:03.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and take Zeref to the evacuation area.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.41,0:02:04.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.22,0:02:06.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.57,0:02:09.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray-sama's voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:13.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, to be awakened by Gray-sama's voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.69,0:02:16.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In whose sheets does Juvia awaken this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.94,0:02:18.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.26,0:02:23.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Power of Life
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.71,0:02:26.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia, chase after them!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.60,0:02:28.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let them have Zeref!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.02,0:02:29.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As you wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.72,0:02:35.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Leg is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.38,0:02:36.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.48,0:02:38.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.65,0:02:40.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's your order, Gray-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.55,0:02:45.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...pain means nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.56,0:02:48.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you, Juvia.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.48,0:03:00.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Make Lance!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.05,0:03:05.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Advance that ice's time to the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.85,0:03:08.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Vaporize!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.94,0:03:15.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Time Ark?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.24,0:03:16.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.18,0:03:21.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't work on humans, but I heard it's a Lost Magic that can manipulate time at will.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.30,0:03:25.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray might be fighting her at the moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.70,0:03:27.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Maker Magic wouldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.90,0:03:30.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye... That's gonna be a tough match-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.17,0:03:32.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Natsu was totally beat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.51,0:03:34.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I wasn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.18,0:03:37.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, even if Gray ran into that cross-dressing geezer,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.64,0:03:39.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,we don't have time to go saving him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.53,0:03:40.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not like I wanna, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:42.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.59,0:03:46.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If it were me, I'd beat 'em by myself, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.63,0:03:47.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't want anyone gettin' in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.88,0:03:51.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, what a long friendship... Totally in sync...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.26,0:03:52.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like you can tell what the other's thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.53,0:03:54.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That ain't it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.04,0:03:57.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, what about a cross-dressing geezer?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.62,0:04:00.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a geezer when I met him on Galuna Island...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.75,0:04:02.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, what a shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.80,0:04:06.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wasn't the old man the disguise?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.00,0:04:10.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I definitely get a "young Master Bob" feel to the guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.02,0:04:11.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely a guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.76,0:04:14.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I feel sorry for Gray.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.72,0:04:17.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna get killed the next time you run into the guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.94,0:04:20.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.93,0:04:22.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A pitfall, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.30,0:04:25.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For when the enemy is in pursuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.83,0:04:29.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, not that... Why are you in a swimsuit?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.04,0:04:30.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.44,0:04:31.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And also, it is fanservice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.62,0:04:32.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For who?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.75,0:04:36.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I was thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.31,0:04:39.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really the time for us to be chatting so casually?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.03,0:04:41.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not one to talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.08,0:04:43.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack and defend... Two teams...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.32,0:04:45.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess it's time to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.19,0:04:50.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's get back to business already, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.17,0:04:51.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying this is my fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.90,0:04:53.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Punishment time, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.16,0:04:54.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.67,0:05:01.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Make Hammer!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.28,0:05:02.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.16,0:05:05.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.90,0:05:09.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Magic doesn't work?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.45,0:05:11.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.46,0:05:22.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I learned Time Ark in order to kill Maker Magic wizards like my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.71,0:05:28.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In order... to kill Ul?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.99,0:05:51.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I hated her for so long...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.29,0:05:57.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.52,0:06:02.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Flash Forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.26,0:06:12.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ul cared for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.18,0:06:14.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.19,0:06:21.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's sad she can't show those feelings anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.48,0:06:32.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't use ice, you'll go hand-to-hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.31,0:06:36.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll beat you with ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.88,0:06:42.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will beat you with Ul's magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.47,0:06:47.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My magic, Time Ark, can manipulate the time of objects.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.16,0:06:51.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Move ice to its future and it vaporizes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.11,0:06:53.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Move ice to its past, and it becomes water.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.25,0:06:59.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe in Ul's Maker Magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.18,0:07:03.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice cannot defeat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.19,0:07:08.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maker Magic won't be of any use at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.25,0:07:29.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.92,0:07:30.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.83,0:07:33.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...will seal away...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.30,0:07:33.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...will seal away...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.39,0:07:36.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...your darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.39,0:07:36.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...your darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.44,0:07:43.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice isn't going to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.55,0:07:48.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.65,0:07:51.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...move its time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.92,0:07:53.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, how?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.63,0:07:58.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't be able to manipulate the time of living things...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.48,0:08:02.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Red ice... Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.62,0:08:08.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He froze his own blood?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.02,0:08:11.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Blade: Seven Strike Dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.18,0:08:23.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cutting the flesh, breaking off the bones...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.89,0:08:26.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What persistence...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.15,0:08:28.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.56,0:08:31.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.15,0:08:36.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.64,0:08:40.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That pose...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.62,0:08:44.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not until I've gone to the World of Great Magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.78,0:08:47.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Make:
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.38,0:08:50.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Rozen Krone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.77,0:08:57.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the exact same Maker Magic as Ul!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.74,0:09:04.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maker Magic is magic that's free.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.98,0:09:07.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For each and every person, it takes a different form.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.45,0:09:11.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Find your own form...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.86,0:09:15.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do, then you can be as strong as anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.34,0:09:23.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought... I would be able to see it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.25,0:09:27.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ul's magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.88,0:09:32.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I suppose so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.50,0:09:35.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The same blood runs in them, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.97,0:09:39.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.92,0:09:45.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.92,0:09:51.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.03,0:09:56.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why have you become like this? Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.68,0:09:57.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.25,0:10:00.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You couldn't even hope to understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.38,0:10:05.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.56,0:10:09.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...abandoned by my mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.16,0:10:31.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom... Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.54,0:10:34.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.13,0:10:40.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.10,0:10:46.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was abandoned by my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.48,0:10:52.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultear-sama, we have come to pick you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.63,0:10:57.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And, the place I was sent...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.40,0:11:01.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's my mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.46,0:11:03.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mother has gone home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.74,0:11:10.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mother requested that we strengthen your magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.13,0:11:11.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.59,0:11:13.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the the Bureau of Magic Development.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.35,0:11:17.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a wonderful facility that invents a range of new magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.88,0:11:21.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, please go into your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.29,0:11:22.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.32,0:11:27.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Until your magic is strengthened, you cannot see your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.63,0:11:29.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what she requested.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.70,0:11:31.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A change of clothes is prepared for you inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.22,0:11:33.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We will call for you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.71,0:11:40.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.79,0:11:43.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.98,0:11:46.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.54,0:11:49.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultear-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.54,0:11:51.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.20,0:12:00.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.76,0:12:02.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.90,0:12:04.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.61,0:12:06.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We are strengthening your magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.74,0:12:09.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It may hurt a little. Please bear with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.56,0:12:12.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Think of it as for your mother's sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.83,0:12:16.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.92,0:12:32.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.45,0:12:36.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No... I won't go...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.19,0:12:37.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.54,0:12:44.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How goes it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.75,0:12:46.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She is quite the vessel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.58,0:12:49.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot even compare her to the other test subjects.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.75,0:12:51.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.56,0:12:53.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She is the daughter of Ul,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.82,0:12:57.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,who is said to be near the level of one of the 10 Great Wizard Saints...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.37,0:12:59.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Increase the level by a factor of 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.35,0:13:02.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Inject the magic power for one hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.28,0:13:04.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.03,0:13:04.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.47,0:13:16.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna go home...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.57,0:13:19.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, come and get me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.90,0:13:22.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.20,0:13:25.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.36,0:13:38.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Test subject 3373 is escaping!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.53,0:13:41.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We've detected an extreme rise in magic power!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.46,0:13:43.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.38,0:13:46.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave her be for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.59,0:13:51.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see what happens, daughter of Ul...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.14,0:13:53.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.26,0:13:54.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.12,0:14:01.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My mind and heart were in tatters
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.53,0:14:04.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,after being subjected to magic power enhancing experiments again and again...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.19,0:14:09.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I continued running, only wishing to see my mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.32,0:14:16.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But... what I saw there...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.32,0:14:35.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...was my mother, looking happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.59,0:14:46.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She abandoned me, and started living a happy life with different children...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.65,0:14:53.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Never forgive...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.35,0:15:02.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I returned to the Bureau of Magic Development as a test subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.37,0:15:07.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to get magic power, and get revenge on my mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.39,0:15:12.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Never forgive...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.86,0:15:17.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Never forgive...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.39,0:15:20.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.98,0:15:21.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.55,0:15:26.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The past few days, her magic power has increased abnormally rapidly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.81,0:15:29.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We think going any further may be dangerous...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.17,0:15:31.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.76,0:15:36.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought she could be a candidate for one of the five, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.36,0:15:40.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The nature of her magic is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.76,0:15:43.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Performing a Body Link with her and myself may be impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.74,0:15:47.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Raise the level to the maximum.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.56,0:15:51.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, there is danger of an explosion...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.01,0:15:51.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not care.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.57,0:15:55.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have obtained all the magic I require.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.98,0:15:58.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no more need for this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.66,0:16:02.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will leave Ul's daughter as a parting gift for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.74,0:16:06.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He disappeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.77,0:16:08.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, we've got trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.89,0:16:10.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The magic power is flowing in reverse!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.61,0:16:12.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.08,0:16:13.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Evacuate!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.24,0:16:14.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Evacuate!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.29,0:16:35.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Before long, I came to learn of the existence of Zeref,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.36,0:16:38.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and a Dark Guild who was after him...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.10,0:16:42.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When Zeref is resurrected once again,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.68,0:16:46.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,the World of Great Magic will be complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.51,0:16:49.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,World of Great Magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.65,0:16:54.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There, all magic can be used freely...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.94,0:16:59.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There is even magic that will allow you to get back happiness which was lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.77,0:17:04.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic to get back lost happiness?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.50,0:17:07.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Time Ark.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.71,0:17:11.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will train you to use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.18,0:17:17.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In this world, Time Ark cannot be said to be complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.55,0:17:22.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is an ancient Lost Magic which has been forgotten...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.82,0:17:28.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, in the World of Great Magic, Time Ark will be complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.44,0:17:33.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can can become someone who voyages through time...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.80,0:17:48.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to do it all again...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.67,0:17:53.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To change this accursed life to one of happiness...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.23,0:17:59.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will complete the World of Great Magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.66,0:18:03.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, save her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.96,0:18:07.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.41,0:18:12.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Save her, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.39,0:18:14.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.28,0:18:19.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Her magic power has been too great ever since she was born!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.64,0:18:24.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,These are... my mother's memories?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.73,0:18:29.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The magic power is concentrated in her tiny body,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.53,0:18:31.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and her fever won't go down!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.59,0:18:37.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, there's a special facility...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.37,0:18:43.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My mother's memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.46,0:18:48.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.15,0:18:57.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My mother, who melted on Galuna Island and flowed into the sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.67,0:19:02.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.10,0:19:10.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is... inside my mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.67,0:19:12.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.56,0:19:15.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, she's dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.35,0:19:18.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.50,0:19:21.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.18,0:19:25.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's dead, and that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.91,0:19:30.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You were supposed to cure her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.36,0:19:34.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you specialized in this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.93,0:19:36.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.29,0:19:41.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We apologize, but her magic power was just too strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.29,0:19:44.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was beyond our ability to cope with.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.44,0:19:46.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's better for you not to see the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.23,0:19:48.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.41,0:19:50.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.71,0:19:53.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me back my daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.26,0:19:56.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Give Ultear back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.17,0:19:58.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's different...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.59,0:20:04.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's different than what I remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.84,0:20:08.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Make Gungnir!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.19,0:20:38.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard Ul speak about you, once.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.27,0:20:48.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When she was born, I felt like a light had flown into my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.33,0:20:54.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My dreams were filled with her bright future...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.70,0:20:58.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was... so very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.15,0:21:05.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The infinite possible futures her tiny body held...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.13,0:21:08.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The power of life...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.92,0:21:12.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My overflowing tears just wouldn't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.81,0:21:21.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to go to the World of Great Magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.73,0:21:27.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and go back to who I was before I hated my mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.24,0:21:31.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She was the proof of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.86,0:21:35.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My tear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.23,0:21:38.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ul...tear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.90,0:21:47.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to see you once again, Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.62,0:22:01.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My battle is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.11,0:22:04.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My battle ain't over yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.04,0:22:08.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't beat Hades.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.41,0:22:10.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't seem like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.28,0:22:14.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not gonna be possible on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.75,0:23:57.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The weather seems like it's getting worse...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.90,0:24:00.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just settin' the stage for a thrilling climax!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.97,0:24:02.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gettin' fired up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.38,0:24:06.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If it keeps raining like this, won't that halve your power, Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.40,0:24:07.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, that's definitely gonna be a problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.91,0:24:10.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You sayin' some {\i1}rain{\i0}'s gonna put out my flames?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.41,0:24:13.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That delayed reaction... We don't do that style gag much.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.84,0:24:16.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Thunder Roar!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.93,0:24:20.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And wait, it's time for the boss fight, not some comedy routine!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.11,0:24:22.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're aware this is just a routine?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.24,0:24:24.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, and I wish I wasn't!
